Thaila Zucchi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thaila_Zucchi 0 Thaila Lucia Zucchi ( [luˈtʃiːa dˈdzukki]; born 19 January 1981) is a British singer and actress of English and Italian descent. She began her career as a member of the British band allSTARS* before transitioning into acting, appearing in Big Brother 8 in the UK, where she played the part of fake Australian housemate Pauline. She has also appeared in Balls of Steel and Star Stories. Thaila_Lucia_Zucchi ( [ luˈtʃiːa_dˈdzukki_] ; born_19_January_1981 ) is a_British_singer_and_actress of English and Italian_descent .
